Global Intelligent Rearview Mirror Market Insights
Intelligent Rearview Mirror Market Market size was valued at USD 1.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 3.0 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 14.0% from 2024 to 2030.

Intelligent Rearview Mirror Market Overview
The global intelligent rearview mirror market is expected to grow significantly in the coming years, driven by increasing demand for enhanced safety features, advanced driver assistance systems (ADAS), and technological advancements in the automotive sector. The market size is projected to reach USD 8.52 billion by 2030, expanding at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 12.6% from 2023 to 2030. The growing adoption of smart and connected vehicles, along with rising consumer preference for improved driving experiences, contributes to the rapid growth of this market. Additionally, technological innovations, such as augmented reality (AR) integration and video streaming capabilities in rearview mirrors, are expected to fuel market growth across both developed and emerging economies.

